5:
Where are Sven and Nimbus? I
haven't those two around today.
14:
Huh, Nimbus is actually going
through with that training.
27:
Wow! Incredible! So cool!
You're the best, Master Nimbus!
31:
How many times do I gotta tell you?
Never take your eyes off your enemy!
41:
I was distracted by you! You look
JUST like Whitetail when you fight...
45:
*sigh* Whatever.
If you're gonna keep dawdling
around here, I'm just gonna leave
you behind.
67:
It's nothing! It's the least I can do,
especially if I want to become as
strong as the legendary Whitetail!
72:
Are you able to walk?
Oy, ratboy. Let's head to the surface.
74:
Please wait!
My companion, he... is still in here.
The monsters...
76:
I was the only one... who made it
out...
79:
Don't worry, miss, leave it to me!
I'll go help your friend!
84:
No, you won't—head back to the
guild and call for help. I've got this.
88:
B-but... I want to go fight alongside
you, Master...
90: You think you're up to it?
96:
I'm asking if you're ready to take the
final step. This ain't no fairy tale
we're walkin' into. I wanna know if
you've got what it takes.
97:
You might die.
Others might die.
Are you prepared for that?
100:
I don't know if I am... but I do know
that if I don't go through with this,
people will get hurt!
104: So, I have to do it! I'm going with you!
108:
All right.
Sorry for puttin' you through a test
like that, kid.
115:
Also, we're still in the midways. You
won't be dyin' any time soon, so
relax.
122:
Nuff talking. Let's get a move on,
Sven!
150:
The little guy looks totally spent!
What happened?
153:
Heh. We made it to the edge of the
midways. Just the two of us.
157: What's with the big grin on your face?
160:
Well. At least Sven is sleeping it off
well. He seems so happy just lying
there.
162: He's a merry little mouse, ain't he.
165:
But he certainly does give it his all.
That much I can't deny.
